--------------------------------------


Steps to set up

1. Create virtual environment and install dependencies
python -m venv venv_wtg_backend
python -m pip install -r requirements.txt
pip uninstall python-magic
pip install python-magic-bin

2. Create database through pgadmin -> docker

3. Update db settings and migrate
postgres://user:password@localhost:5432/wtg_backend
python .\manage.py migrate

4. Create superuser
python .\manage.py createsuperuser
superuser@saleor.com superuser   

uvicorn --reload saleor.asgi:application



--------------------


App installation
Install stripe through graphql playground and python manage.py runserver
Afterwards, run server with uvicorn and configure through saleor_dashboard

Must activate email plugin through saleor_dashboard